HEADWORD: Yttriferous
<hw>Yt*trif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Bearing or
containing yttrium or the allied elements; <as>as, gadolinite is one of
the <ex>yttriferous</ex> minerals</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yttrious</ent>⟦br⟧
